---
title: Ancho BBQ Burgers with Griddled Onion & Roasted Broccoli
description: Ready to amp up burger night? Meet ancho—the slightly spicier chili powder of your BBQ dreams. Here you’ll mix it with tangy red pepper jam and BBQ sauce for a savory slather on toasted buns. Sandwiched between all that flavor are juicy beef patties and tender smoky onion rounds. And since none of these flavors can go to waste, you’ll mix the remaining ancho BBQ sauce with mayo for a creamy potato wedge dipper. This definitely ancho average burger!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/62c58dff4f9056cd0e0ac834-e1208354.jpg
